::Zardus/Bloodystrike::

A slight smile creeps across Zardus' face as the images enter his head, a 
small chuckle escaping his lips. Zardus supresses the laugh, looking at 
Skulletron.

"Very good. Very good indeed."

He looks at Bloodystrike, the other nodding and walking off. Zardus looks 
back at Skulletron.

"Very well, follow me to the conference room, I can use the projectors there 
to explain the mission."

Zardus walks off, heading for the conference room, slightly pausing for the 
two others to follow him.
